Summary: Biochemical reaction from docetaxel metabolite m1/m3 to docetaxel metabolite m4. This interaction is catalyzed by CYP3A4.
Biochemical reaction from docetaxel to docetaxel metabolite m1/m3. This interaction can be catalyzed by CYP3A4 or CYP3A5.
Transport from docetaxel to docetaxel. This interaction can be catalyzed by ABCG2, ABCC2 or ABCB1.
Transport from docetaxel to docetaxel. This interaction is catalyzed by SLCO1B3.
